properties.name: data
properties.description: An object with updated row fields.

properties.name: insertAfterKey
properties.description: A key that identifies a record after which a new record should be inserted. Applies only if the [type] is *"insert"*.

properties.name: insertBeforeKey
properties.description: A key that identifies the record before which a new record should be inserted. Applies only if the [type] is *"insert"*.

properties.name: key
properties.description: The key of the row being created, updated, or removed.
